import React from 'react'
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'

// import { LOGOUT_USER } from '../utils/mutations'


const Navbar = () => (

    <nav>
      <NavLink exact activeClassName="active" className="home-link icon" to="/">
        <FontAwesomeIcon icon="fa-solid fa-house" color="white" />
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink activeClassName="active" className="contact-link icon" to="/contact">
        <FontAwesomeIcon icon="fa-solid fa-address-book" color="white" />
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink activeClassName="active" className="login-link icon" to="/login">
        <FontAwesomeIcon icon="fa-solid fa-exclamation" color="white" />
      </NavLink>
    </nav>
)


export default Navbar;
